  "title": "Architect / Architect Manager",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibilities:</u></p>\n<p>· Help to lead architecture design and execution throughout the project cycle.</p>\n<p>· Oversee progress of on-site work ensure project is built according to design plans and resolve any issues that may arise.</p>\n<p>· Work with clients, consultants and stakeholders to ensure that the building plan meet the</p>\n<p>necessary building codes and regulations.</p>\n<p>· Ensure key deadlines are met and staff are working together effectively</p>\n<p>· May manage various groups of architects, technicians and/or specialists.</p>\n<p><u>Requirements:</u></p>\n<p>· Bachelor’s/ Master’s Degree in Architecture or related fields</p>\n<p>· Minimum 6 years of relevant architectural experience</p>\n<p>· Being registered with Singapore Board of Architects would be an advantage</p>\n<p>· Good knowledge of architectural details, working drawings and construction practices</p>\n<p>· Conversant with local code and regulations</p>\n<p>· Competency in authority requirements and submission procedures</p>\n<p>· Ability to lead a team</p>\n<p>· Experience in high density housing and/or public housing</p>\n<p>· Good leadership and communication skill</p>",
