    "description": "<p>\r\n\tCONSORTIUM 168 ARCHITECTS PTE LTD</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tConsortium 168 is a mid-sized architectural practice based in Singapore. Since 1982, we have produced many award-winning works and have established ourselves as a reputed architectural firm in Singapore.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tHere at C168, we strongly believe in building connections in our architecture and striving to create environments that impact people’s lives positively.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tOur people are our most important assets and we place much emphasis on their development and welfare.  We are looking for talented individuals who share our passion and desire in producing great works to join us.</p>\r\n",
